] Return icon name\n\n### Backlog and Roadmap\n<a href=\"https://github.com/orgs/open-imx/projects/4/\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/orgs/open-imx/projects/4/</a>\n\n## Supported Python Versions\n\n!!! warning  \n    ***Python Typehints are awesome therefor 3.9 and below will NOT be supported***.\n\n## Quick Start\nTODO\n\n## Distribution and installation\nJust install the library\n\n```pip install imxIcons```\n\nhttps://github.com/open-imx/imxIconsApi\nfor a demo see: https://imx-icons-api.azurewebsites.net/\n\n\n## Code samples and snippets\nTODO\n\n## Contributing\nContributions welcome! [Join our Discord Community](https://discord.gg/wBses7bPFg) \n\n~~For more information on the design of the library, see [contribution guidelines for this project](CONTRIBUTING.md).~~\n"], "modules": [{"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.add_arrow_marker", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "sign", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.entities_path", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.imx_version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.RS300", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.RS301", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.RS301B", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.signs", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx500.sign_icon_entities_v500", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx124", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "imxIcons.domain.sign.sign_imx124.add_arrow_marker", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "sign", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": nu